tp - Total power - average chans in stack1 weighted by cal in stack3

EXAMPLES:

gt ca:;st 3;gt dt:;tp	Get a cal scan in stack 3 and use it to weight the
			next data scan and print the continuum antenna
			temperature.

DESCRIPTION:

Tp is used to derive continuum data from observations with a spectrometer.
It weights the channels correctly for the best snr.
